# Application Configuration for My Auth 2.0 OIDC\n\nThis file contains the necessary configuration for the My Auth 2.0 OIDC application.\n\n## Configuration Parameters\n- `client_id`: Your client ID here.\n- `client_secret`: Your client secret here.\n- `redirect_uri`: The URL to redirect to after authentication.\n- `authorization_endpoint`: The authorization endpoint for the OIDC provider.\n- `token_endpoint`: The token endpoint for the OIDC provider.\n- `userinfo_endpoint`: The endpoint that returns info about the authenticated user.\n\n## Example Configuration\n\n```json\n{\n  "client_id": "your_client_id",\n  "client_secret": "your_client_secret",\n  "redirect_uri": "https://yourapp.com/redirect",\n  "authorization_endpoint": "https://provider.com/oauth/authorize",\n  "token_endpoint": "https://provider.com/oauth/token",\n  "userinfo_endpoint": "https://provider.com/userinfo"\n}\n```\n